            "title": "滬深北交所齊將融資保證金比例由80%升至100%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上海、深圳、北京證券交易所中午公布，經中國證監會批准，落實將投資者融資買入證券時的融資保證金最低比例，由80%提高至100%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581282-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%a4%e6%89%80%e9%bd%8a%e5%b0%87%e8%9e%8d%e8%b3%87%e4%bf%9d%e8%ad%89%e9%87%91%e6%af%94%e4%be%8b%e7%94%b180%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3100",
